  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">不朽鬼婆芭芭</span>·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">雅嘎的造物違逆了凡間魔法的法則。在她所有臭名昭著的勞什子里，讓她在無盡</span><span class=\"GramE\">的諸界中</span>鞏固傳奇惡名的神器乃是能夠助她穿越位面的：<em>芭芭·雅嘎</em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>的臼與杵</em></span><em>Baba Yaga</em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>』</em></span><em>s Mortar and Pestle</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。這兩件芭芭</span>·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">雅</span><span class=\"GramE\">嘎</span>特色鮮明的工具各是一件需要同調的單一神器。若兩物件分開，那麼<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>杵Pestle</em></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">會在下一個黎明出現在</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>臼Mortar</em></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">旁邊。</span>  <br /><br /><em><strong>隨機屬性</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。這件神器具有以下隨機屬性，你可以通過對著<em>《地下城主指南》</em>中的</span>「<span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>神器</em></span> 」<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">章節擲</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>以決定它們。</p><ul><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">兩項弱效增益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一項強效增益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一項弱效減益屬性</span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br /><em><strong>臼的屬性</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。臼是一個微型的小木碗。然而，臼的大小會隨著你放進去的任何需要它容納的東西而擴展、增大至其上限大型</span>——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">如果它周圍的空間足夠的話。這意味著它甚至裝得下一個大型生物。</span><br /><em><strong>杵的屬性</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。</span><span class=\"GramE\">杵是一根</span>六英尺長的破木棒。每回合一次，當你持握著杵時，你可以使其伸長至一根長棍或使其縮回一根杵（無需動作）。作為長棍時，<span class=\"GramE\">杵是一個</span>在攻擊擲<span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>與傷害擲<span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>上有+3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">加值的魔法武器。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">杵有</span>12<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能。當你</span><span class=\"GramE\">使用杵並以</span>一次近戰攻擊命中時，你可以消耗至多3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能以額外造成每發充能</span>1d8<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">力場傷害。杵在每天黎明時恢復所有已消耗的充能。</span><br /><em><strong>完美工具</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。當你同時持握著</span><span class=\"GramE\">杵與臼</span>時，你可以用動作來說出任何一種非魔法的植物、礦物或液體的名字，這些材料的價格需為10gp<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">或更低。</span><span class=\"GramE\">臼</span>立刻會充滿指定價格數的那種材料。使用后，直到完成<span class=\"GramE\">一</span>次長休前，你無法再次使用這個動作。<br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">你還可以將這件神器作為鍊金工具，釀酒工具，廚師工具，草藥工具或</span><span class=\"GramE\">毒師工具</span>使用。你在將這件神器作為以上幾種工具使用時所進行的任何檢定上具有優勢。<br /><em><strong>原初分解</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。當杵和</span><span class=\"GramE\">臼都</span>在你的5<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">尺之內時，作為一個動作，你可以命令</span><span class=\"GramE\">杵</span>開始搗碎作業。杵會自行行動，將臼中容納的物品搗成均能夠<span class=\"GramE\">同等用於</span>烹調或鍊金的漿糊或精細粉末，持續1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">分鐘或你用一個動作來口頭命令它停止。在你的回合開始時，任何處於臼內的東西會受到</span>4d10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">力場傷害。若目標生命</span><span class=\"GramE\">值因此</span>降至0<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">，則其會被搗成適宜的粉末、肉</span><span class=\"GramE\">漿或者</span>漿糊。只有魔法物品不受影響。若你願意，你可以在<span class=\"GramE\">杵停止</span>工作時讓臼把它的內容物分開成不同堆，比如骨粉和骨粉放在一起，藥末與藥末堆在一起，尚在搏動的機體器官堆在一起。<br /><em><strong>黑夜穿梭</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。若你在臼內持握著杵，你可以用動作發出口頭命令，</span><span class=\"GramE\">讓臼穿穿梭</span>到一處特定的地點或一個特定的生物處。你不需要知道你的目標在什麼位置，但你的目標必須是一個特定的位置——<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">不可以僅僅是</span>「<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">最近的河流</span>」<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">或</span>「<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一條紅龍的巢穴</span>」<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。若被選定的目標在你的</span>1000<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">英里內，</span><span class=\"GramE\">臼就會飛</span>向空中而後消失。你與任何處於臼內的生物會穿過一道夢境般的天穹，朦朧的世界映像在你的下方閃過。其他生物可能看見你在夜空中穿梭於你的原點與目標位置之間的影像。你會在1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">小時後，或在夜間</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">分鐘後到達目的地。</span><br /><em><strong>死馬識途</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。當你在命令</span><span class=\"GramE\">臼</span>穿行之時，你可以轉而擲出一把附著<span class=\"GramE\">在臼底的</span>粉末或肉漿，然後說出一個其他存在位面的位置或物質位面的一個其他世界。若那材料來自於那個位面或世界的一個生物，<span class=\"GramE\">那麼臼上的</span>旅行者會穿過一道純凈的夜空，而後在一分鐘內出現在目標位置的一處未被佔據的位置。<br /><em><strong>摧毀臼和</strong></em><span class=\"GramE\"><em><strong>杵</strong></em></span><span style=\"FONT-WEIGHT:normal;FONT-STYLE:normal\"><em><strong>。</strong></em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">若杵和</span><span class=\"GramE\">臼被</span>芭芭·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">雅嘎的步行小屋或芭芭</span>·<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">雅</span><span class=\"GramE\">嘎本鬼</span>婆踩在底下並被擠壓，它們會被摧毀。<br /></p></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
